<paragraph id="F004581BD3388AAFDB6086028C4561FA" pageId="8" pageNumber="85">Body length: 23.3; pronotum length: 5.9; pronotum height: 4.9; hind femur: 20.2; tegmina: 37.2.</paragraph>
